Video Screensaver for IGEL OS.


Videoscreensaver offer an alternative to IGEL Default screen saver, allowing to play videos and or still image slideshows - by filename order or random. 
Additionally you can protect the screensaver with a PIN code. 

Changelog:

Initial Release 1.0.0

Videos to be placed in /userhome/videoscreensaver
Pictures to be paced in /userome/videoscreensaverpics

Use IGEL Setup to configure inactivity time out, play list order, pin code and picture duration. Videos will play in full length. 

